fields.name: Buffalo Reaper Mower 145cm/13mm
fields.description: The two-piece Buffalo pool cue Reaper Mower has a striking decal design. The Buffalo pool cue has a good price-quality ratio and is very suitable for novice players. The Reaper Mower pool cue has a total length of 145 cm and a 13 mm tip.

fields.name: Fury Destroyer DM-04 Black
fields.description:
2-piece pool cue from Fury from the Destroyer Series.
The Destroyer is characterized by the beautiful design, the streoeve handle and the Treu-Loc closure.
The stainless steel Buttring with lasered DESTROYER logo emphasizes the durability and strength of the brand.

fields.name: Adam George Balabushka nr.6
fields.description: This classic cue features a maple forearm with beautiful, natural birds eye patterns, four large and four small inlaid flames of split ebony, inlaid with ivorine diamonds and a double silver ring with chessboard pattern in ivorine and ebony in the forearm and butt. Features a brushed stainless steel pilot joint and two nickel rings with Bushka-style block patterns.

fields.name: Maxton Ionics J/B
fields.description:
This Maxton Ionics has a minimalist design. Simple but powerful, black with black rings, and matte stainless steel butt cap.
 

The Maxton Iobic Break-Jump cue is equipped with a comfortable Soft Touch Grip in black leatherette, and a high-gloss joint. Equipped with a high impact composite Break-Jump ferrule.

fields.name: Mc Dermott Lucky L58 Magenta
fields.description:
Lucky pool cues are designed, developed, and distributed exclusively by McDermott Cue

IN STOCK
The Mc Dermott Lucky pool cues consist of a blend of premium maple wood and intricate graphic overlays.
These properties give you exceptional value for pool cues.
These cues have one of the most solid hits of the globally produced pool cues in the industry.

fields.name: Piranha S2 nr.1
fields.description:
Beginner's cue with exclusive designs and a sleek UV high-gloss finish. Quality stainless steel pilot joint in mirror finish, black nylon grip, high impact composite ferrule and Laperti tip.

fields.name: Triton S2 nr.1
fields.description: The Triton S2 No. 1 pool cue consists of two parts and is a good cue for beginners. The cue has a reinforced top of maple and has a single wooden connection to the bottom end. The weight can be increased by screwing in a weight screw in the bottom end.

fields.name: Harley Davidson towel
fields.description: Soaked with nostalgic attitude, this versatile, retro inspired Harley-Davidson® towel is jacquard loomed of 500 grams per square meter of 100% absorbent terry cotton. A metal grommet and loop make it easy to hang in a convenient location Put this towel on your golf bag, pool cue bag, in the garage or anywhere you might need a hand towel.
